Package com.android

Interface Transport<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
Aeroplane, Boat, Car, Train
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface
public interface Transport<T>
marks this interface as a functional interface which then can be used in a lambda if you want has one abstract method void drive that takes a generic type T, and each class uses a number of techniques to give a type To T To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
See Also:
Car, Boat, Aeroplane, Train
